[
  {
    "startTime": 5.66,
    "endTime": 6.28,
    "text": "Bruce."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.28,
    "endTime": 8.96,
    "text": "I think I've been playing too much Pokémon GO."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.96,
    "endTime": 9.680000000000001,
    "text": "Interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.68,
    "endTime": 12.959999999999999,
    "text": "Because right now it looks like there is a giant Pikachu sitting next to you..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.96,
    "endTime": 14.34,
    "text": "wearing a Sherlock Holmes hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.34,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "While I do think you are playing WAY too much Pokémon..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 18.26,
    "text": "I'm happy to report..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 19.880000000000003,
    "text": "You are not seeing things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.88,
    "endTime": 20.68,
    "text": "Say what now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.82,
    "endTime": 22.94,
    "text": "There is in fact a Pikachu..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.94,
    "endTime": 25.220000000000002,
    "text": "sitting next to me in a Sherlock Holmes hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.36,
    "endTime": 27.66,
    "text": "WHAAAAAAAAAAAAT!?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.66,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "That thing is real?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 29.76,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.2,
    "endTime": 31.939999999999998,
    "text": "A real life Pikachu?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.06,
    "endTime": 32.300000000000004,
    "text": "Yes it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.3,
    "endTime": 34.16,
    "text": "You're telling me I'm looking at a real Pikachu?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.16,
    "endTime": 34.919999999999995,
    "text": "That's what I said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.92,
    "endTime": 36.22,
    "text": "He's really excited!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.22,
    "endTime": 36.92,
    "text": "We call it fangirling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.92,
    "endTime": 38.42,
    "text": "Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.68,
    "endTime": 39.72,
    "text": "This is so cool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.4,
    "endTime": 41.86,
    "text": "Hello, Pikachu!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.02,
    "endTime": 43.18,
    "text": "I am so exciting to m.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.18,
    "endTime": 43.78,
    "text": "I mean..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.1,
    "endTime": 46.1,
    "text": "It is so exciting to meet you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.22,
    "endTime": 47.24,
    "text": "(Pika Pika!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.36,
    "endTime": 47.98,
    "text": "(Pikachu!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.98,
    "endTime": 49.04,
    "text": "I know right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.04,
    "endTime": 50.12,
    "text": "Where did he come from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.66,
    "endTime": 51.63999999999999,
    "text": "From Pokémon. Duh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.72,
    "endTime": 52.82,
    "text": "I know that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.82,
    "endTime": 54.22,
    "text": "I mean why do you have him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.22,
    "endTime": 55.76,
    "text": "Is he yours?  Did you catch him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.82,
    "endTime": 57.14,
    "text": "No, he's not mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.14,
    "endTime": 59.160000000000004,
    "text": "He's just a detective for some reason."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.46,
    "endTime": 63.28,
    "text": "So I guess he came here because he wants advice from the greatest detective of all time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.9,
    "endTime": 64.84,
    "text": "(Pikachu?)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.96,
    "endTime": 66.39999999999999,
    "text": "No!  Not from Columbo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.18,
    "endTime": 67.74000000000001,
    "text": "From Me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.2,
    "endTime": 69.64,
    "text": "You snarky fuzz ball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.88,
    "endTime": 70.8,
    "text": "(Peeka)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.92,
    "endTime": 71.44,
    "text": "Watch it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.44,
    "endTime": 71.94,
    "text": "(Chu!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.94,
    "endTime": 72.74,
    "text": "Hold on.  Wait a second!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.74,
    "endTime": 73.94,
    "text": "You can understand him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.94,
    "endTime": 75.12,
    "text": "Of course I can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.12,
    "endTime": 76.48,
    "text": "Because I'm batman!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.48,
    "endTime": 79.18,
    "text": "Apparently the only one who can are me and the kid from Jurassic World."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.18,
    "endTime": 80.26,
    "text": "(Pika Pika)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.28,
    "endTime": 81.48,
    "text": "What is he saying?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.48,
    "endTime": 82.78,
    "text": "Ah just detective stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.78,
    "endTime": 84.86,
    "text": "He also sounds exactly like Deadpool..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.86,
    "endTime": 86.02,
    "text": "which is really weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.02,
    "endTime": 87.56,
    "text": "What's so weird about sounding like Deadpool?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.56,
    "endTime": 89.98,
    "text": "Because Deadpool is nothing like Pikachu!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.06,
    "endTime": 90.56,
    "text": "That's why."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.56,
    "endTime": 91.84,
    "text": "Hey, Dork Knight!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.84,
    "endTime": 93.38000000000001,
    "text": "Not all Pikachus are the same."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.38,
    "endTime": 94.1,
    "text": "Besides..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.3,
    "endTime": 95.1,
    "text": "(Pika Pika)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.32,
    "endTime": 96.32,
    "text": "(Pikachu)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.32,
    "endTime": 98.88,
    "text": "Well I guess you guys sort of do have that in common."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.92,
    "endTime": 99.88,
    "text": "So anyways..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.88,
    "endTime": 103.11999999999999,
    "text": "I'm just teaching him everything he needs to know about being an amazing detective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.12,
    "endTime": 104.82000000000001,
    "text": "Right! Amazing detective!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 105.5,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.5,
    "endTime": 107.12,
    "text": "Feed me, pointy eared man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.12,
    "endTime": 108.66000000000001,
    "text": "Okay.  First thing you need..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.06,
    "endTime": 110.82000000000001,
    "text": "Is a super awesome butler."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.92,
    "endTime": 113.24,
    "text": "Do you have a super awesome butler?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.24,
    "endTime": 114.86,
    "text": "I have a super awesome butt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.86,
    "endTime": 116.8,
    "text": "It shoots out all kinds of electricity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 119.08,
    "text": "Do you have endless amounts of money?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.42,
    "endTime": 121.26,
    "text": "I'm worth about 15 billion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.26,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Is that enough?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.06,
    "endTime": 123.14,
    "text": "It's a start."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.14,
    "endTime": 125.32000000000001,
    "text": "Do you have access to a utility belt?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.5,
    "endTime": 126.32,
    "text": "(Pika)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.32,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Well... We've apparently got a long way to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 130.4,
    "text": "A detective Pikachu..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.4,
    "endTime": 134.1,
    "text": "I just can't believe this is how I'm meeting a real Pokémon for the first time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.1,
    "endTime": 134.66,
    "text": "What do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.66,
    "endTime": 137.22,
    "text": "I don't know.  I just thought it would have been with Ash and Misty..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.22,
    "endTime": 138.26,
    "text": "Or Team Rocket."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 139.72,
    "text": "Certainly not as a detective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.72,
    "endTime": 143.48,
    "text": "I think the Pokémon origin story has been pretty much established."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.48,
    "endTime": 147.22,
    "text": "Plus, I think a real life version of that story would be met with extreme prejudice..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.22,
    "endTime": 148.04,
    "text": "If it wasn't perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.04,
    "endTime": 152.92,
    "text": "What! You think people would reject seeing live action versions of the original Pokémon Cast?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.6,
    "endTime": 155.29999999999998,
    "text": "I can't tell if you're being sarcastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.3,
    "endTime": 155.9,
    "text": "I'm serious!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.9,
    "endTime": 158.46,
    "text": "They're making everything into a movie now. Why not this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.46,
    "endTime": 162.16,
    "text": "I saw this live action trailer of the Lion King earlier and I thought it looked amazing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.36,
    "endTime": 163.3,
    "text": "(Pikachu!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.3,
    "endTime": 165.72,
    "text": "He's right.  That's not live action, dude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 166.8,
    "text": "And second..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.8,
    "endTime": 170.5,
    "text": "I would argue it only looks amazing because you enjoyed the original so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.08,
    "endTime": 171.58,
    "text": "So?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.58,
    "endTime": 173.94000000000003,
    "text": "So powerful music is always powerful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.94,
    "endTime": 175.54,
    "text": "I don't understand why that's bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.54,
    "endTime": 177.5,
    "text": "It means the music is doing the heavy lifting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.5,
    "endTime": 179.32,
    "text": "You of all people should know what that's like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.32,
    "endTime": 180.29999999999998,
    "text": "What? Heavy lifting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.3,
    "endTime": 183.74,
    "text": "No. Powerful music in a trailer hyping up an otherwise average movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.84,
    "endTime": 184.96,
    "text": "-(pika pika) -He He"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.1,
    "endTime": 186.57999999999998,
    "text": "Oh ha ha. Very funny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.62,
    "endTime": 187.66,
    "text": "You don't know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.66,
    "endTime": 190.4,
    "text": "I know making films on established characters is very delicate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.4,
    "endTime": 195.4,
    "text": "So I think leaving the original alone and focusing on the obscure video game title is actually pretty wise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.46,
    "endTime": 196.22,
    "text": "(pika pee!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.38,
    "endTime": 197.18,
    "text": "Exactly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.4,
    "endTime": 201.70000000000002,
    "text": "This way Pikachu gets to have a unique story while still having that precious nostalgia bait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.7,
    "endTime": 204.07999999999998,
    "text": "And it's also a way to capitalize on Ryan Reynolds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.16,
    "endTime": 204.79999999999998,
    "text": "That too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.8,
    "endTime": 205.8,
    "text": "That's kind of sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 207.88,
    "text": "Why does nostalgia bait have to be a thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.88,
    "endTime": 213.1,
    "text": "Because if you can make people remember something they loved when they were younger..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.1,
    "endTime": 214.54,
    "text": "they will get excited..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.78,
    "endTime": 216.6,
    "text": "and want to watch it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.6,
    "endTime": 218.84,
    "text": "Which means the studios will make a lot more money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.86,
    "endTime": 220.22000000000003,
    "text": "The Pokémon gets it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.22,
    "endTime": 222.2,
    "text": "You might be a great detective after all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.42,
    "endTime": 222.92,
    "text": "(Pika Pika)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.92,
    "endTime": 224.61999999999998,
    "text": "That seems like such a gimmick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.62,
    "endTime": 225.8,
    "text": "Who falls for that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.1,
    "endTime": 227.62,
    "text": "Everyone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.62,
    "endTime": 229.6,
    "text": "Well, not me!  I'm not gonna fall for that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.6,
    "endTime": 232.54,
    "text": "I only want to enjoy original stuff from now on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.86,
    "endTime": 236.3,
    "text": "BAAAAAAAAA FRED SAVAGE!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.34,
    "endTime": 238.54,
    "text": "WATCH MY MOVIE YOU GUYS!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.56,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "DEADPOOOOOOOL"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.28,
    "endTime": 242.36,
    "text": "PRINCESS BRIIIIIIIIIIIIIDE."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.14,
    "endTime": 244.89999999999998,
    "text": "Ha! Hey, I know what that is!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.12,
    "endTime": 247.54,
    "text": "That's that guy from that movie I Iiked back in the day!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.58,
    "endTime": 248.70000000000002,
    "text": "That's awesome!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.7,
    "endTime": 250.54,
    "text": "I'm definitely gonna go see that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.8,
    "endTime": 252.08,
    "text": "You see what I mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.56,
    "endTime": 254.12,
    "text": "Oh yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.12,
    "endTime": 254.96,
    "text": "(Peeka-Pee!)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.48,
    "endTime": 256.92,
    "text": "BAAAaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.14,
    "endTime": 258.74,
    "text": "Nostalgiaaaaaaaaaaaa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.74,
    "endTime": 262.6,
    "text": "gonna make monEEEEEEEEEEEEy off your childhooooooooood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.6,
    "endTime": 264.0,
    "text": "Eheeeeeeyaaaaaaaaaaa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.02,
    "endTime": 265.62,
    "text": "Oh, that's riiiiiiight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.14,
    "endTime": 269.02,
    "text": "I'm Deadpool"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.26,
    "endTime": 270.06,
    "text": "I'm Pikachu"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.38,
    "endTime": 271.26,
    "text": "I'm Deadpool"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.6,
    "endTime": 272.40000000000003,
    "text": "I'm Pikachu"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.4,
    "endTime": 274.62,
    "text": "I'm Batman!  That's enough!  I'm Batman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.06,
    "endTime": 277.38,
    "text": "Make me think of that thing I liked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.8,
    "endTime": 280.04,
    "text": "make me think of that thing I liked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.4,
    "endTime": 282.64,
    "text": "make me think of that thing I liked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.9,
    "endTime": 285.14,
    "text": "make me think of that thing I liked"
  }
]